Ward {3}
[i]Bastion of Silence[/i] – During your turn, opponents can't cast spells or activate abilities.
[i]Sworn Protector[/i] – When Gilliam, Wall of Silence enters, look at the top five cards of your library, you may reveal a creature card and exile it. Put the rest on the top of your library in any order. Whenever Gilliam, Wall of Silence leaves the battlefield, put the exiled creature onto the battlefield with an additional shield counter on it.
